"text_bw":"trw~H","text_ar":"تروّح"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of herbage,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became tall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and in like manner said of trees; as well as in well as in another sense explained in the first paragraph. (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taray~uHN","text_ar":"تَرَيُّحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", thought by ISd to be an inf. n., of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taray~aHa","text_ar":"تَرَيَّحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroyaHiy~apN","text_ar":"اَرْيَحِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}